Description:

Live the life of an elite futuristic soldier, from tragic
beginnings to heroic redemption. Aided by high tech weaponry
and close allies, uncover a treacherous conspiracy that 
hreatens what is left of humanity. Will you offer help to 
save civilization from destruction in a post-apocalyptic 
world? Will you join the fight? If so, prepare yourself 
for the fight of a lifetime.


Date: 2012 '12 '08

- Created basic gameloop
- Keyboard implementation
- Render classification
- Bufferstrategy(3): why not (2) because it's better than a double buffer, and its more fluent with rendering and every system will be able to run it (smoothly)
- Timer (console written)
- FPS meter (in the menu bar)(don't know if it works on linux or mac why: because I simpely don't own a mac or linux pc/laptop)

